---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About">
  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:32px;">About Me</h2>
      <div class="about-body">
        <p>Hey, I'm Chris — a software engineer at Google and someone who can't stop building things after hours. This site is where I share what I'm working on, what I'm learning, and what I think about.</p>

        <h2>What I do at Google</h2>
        <p>I work as a software engineer at Google. My day-to-day involves building and scaling software that reaches millions of people. It's a job I genuinely love, but some of my most interesting work happens outside of it.</p>

        <h2>Why this site</h2>
        <p>I wanted a home for my side projects, writing, and eventually YouTube videos. Partly to document things for myself, partly to share with others interested in tech, finance, and building a career in software. Sites like <a href="https://huyenchip.com" target="_blank">Chip Huyen's</a> inspired me to just start.</p>

        <h2>Outside of work</h2>
        <p>When I'm not coding I'm usually reading about investing, building something with a new API, or thinking about financial independence. I'm also getting into creating YouTube content around the topics I care about — videos launching soon.</p>

        <h2>Get in touch</h2>
        <p>
          Best way to reach me is <a href="mailto:chris@duncanc.io">email</a>.
          I'm also on <a href="https://github.com/cduncan" target="_blank">GitHub</a> and
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/chrisduncan" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
